properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 26 at 3:57PM CST until January 27 at 12:00AM CST by NWS Aberdeen SD
properties.description:
* WHAT...Mixed precipitation. Total snow accumulations of up to
one half inch and ice accumulations of a light glaze.

* WHERE...Corson and Dewey Counties.

* WHEN...Until 11 PM MST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Roads and sidewalks may become slippery
through late this evening. If traveling in central or north
central South Dakota, use extra caution and slow down. Allow
for longer braking distances.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

The latest road conditions can be obtained by calling 5 1 1.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FOR A LIGHT WINTRY MIX UNTIL 11 PM MST THIS EVENING
